Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:30.14,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Zero still means zero! But eat up anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to eat away my sorrows!
