Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:43.41,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'll... end... up... sucking... \Naway... everyone's... magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.41,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! We just have to eat more, then!
