Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heading to the royal capital \Nwith her brother with the bangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:10.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,the Captain of the Silver Eagles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry after them!
