Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.70,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good! Keep on chowing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.88,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,And being among them is extra special.
