Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.09,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,That's the power of our new best friend!
