Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.31,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's super badass!
